Anatomical Measures Computation â€“ Computes key metrics such as volume, surface area, and curvature.

Inverse 3D Map to Atlas â€“ Maps individual brain data into a common space for group analysis.

Surface-based Smoothing â€“ Smooths data to reduce noise and improve visualization quality.

