Diffusion Tensor Calculation â€“ Models water diffusion to assess white matter integrity.

ODF Estimation â€“ Determines fiber orientation for visualizing brain connectivity.

DTI Parameter Map Generation â€“ Produces diffusion metrics such as FA and MD for quantitative analysis.

Resampling to Atlas â€“ Standardizes diffusion data for cross-subject and atlas-based studies.

Volumetric Smoothing â€“ Reduces noise and enhances the clarity of diffusion parameter maps.

